How do you make friends?

Well, clothes can play a big part in it.

Let me explain...

When you’re able to reflect your personality through your clothes, you’ll find it makes bonding with like-minded people easier.

Think of your appearance, a first impression, like a movie trailer.

You want to make sure the trailer matches the movie, right? 

People infer what kind of person you are, your interests, if you can be trusted or how competent they think you are from their first glance at your outfit (it happens all within the first 7 seconds).

When you have a distinct style, you'll find similar people gravitate toward you or strike up a conversation.

So make sure your clothes are sending the message you want.

Our stylists can help you hone in on your unique style and build a wardrobe full of premium pieces around that.
